  border-radius: 50%;
  border: 5px solid #0077cc;
}

section {
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}

a {
  color: #0077cc;
  text-decoration: none;
}

a:hover {
  text-decoration: underline;
}
```

> ğŸ¨ Feel free to change colors, fonts, and spacing to match your style!

